7 An Act relating to the Oklahoma Department of
Agriculture, Food, and Forestry; requiring that
8 portions of certain appropriated funds be used for
certain purposes; providing an effective date; and
9 declaring an emergency.
10
11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. From the funds appropriated to the Oklahoma
13 Department of Agriculture, Food, and Forestry in Enrolled House Bill
14 No. 2766 of the 1st Session of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature, the
15 sum of One Million Dollars ($1,000,000.00) shall be used for the
16 Oklahoma State University Robert M. Kerr Food and Agricultural
17 Products Center for operational expenses.
18 SECTION 2. From the funds appropriated to the Oklahoma
19 Department of Agriculture, Food, and Forestry in Enrolled House Bill
20 No. 2766 of the 1st Session of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature, the
21 sum of Five Million Two Hundred Thousand Dollars ($5,200,000.00)
22 shall be used for the extension offices that are affiliated with the
23 Oklahoma State University Cooperative Extension Service.
24
ENGR. S. B. NO. 1153 Page 1
1 SECTION 3. From the funds appropriated to the Oklahoma
2 Department of Agriculture, Food, and Forestry in Enrolled House Bill
3 No. 2766 of the 1st Session of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature, the
4 sum of One Million Three Hundred Thousand Dollars ($1,300,000.00)
5 shall be used for research centers that are affiliated with Oklahoma
6 State University Agriculture Experiment Stations.
7 SECTION 4. From the funds appropriated to the Oklahoma
8 Department of Agriculture, Food, and Forestry in Enrolled House Bill
9 No. 2766 of the 1st Session of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature, the
10 sum of Five Million Five Hundred Thousand Dollars ($5,500,000.00)
11 shall be used for cooperative extension and agriculture research
12 programs that are affiliated with Langston University.
13 SECTION 5. This act shall become effective July 1, 2025.
14 SECTION 6. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
15 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
16 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
17 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
